revision.text:
{{redirect|Template:Weight|body weight|Template:Convert}}
{{Documentation subpage}}
<!-- PLEASE ADD CATEGORIES AND INTERWIKIS AT THE BOTTOM OF THIS PAGE -->__NOTOC__
{{tsh|uwi|weight}}

== Usage ==
*<CODE><NOWIKI>{{undue inline|{{subst:DATE}}}}</NOWIKI></CODE>
*<CODE><NOWIKI>{{undue inline|reason=your justification|{{subst:DATE}}}}</NOWIKI></CODE>
*<CODE><NOWIKI>{{undue inline|1=Talk section|reason=your justification|{{subst:DATE}}}}</NOWIKI></CODE>
Add this template after a fact or [[posit]] to signify that this statement may be giving [[WP:UNDUE|undue weight]] to an idea or point of view. The template may also be used to identify a [[WP:FRINGE|fringe idea]]. To specify a section of the discussion on the talk page, use <code><nowiki>{{undue-inline|talk page section name}}</nowiki></code>.

== Parameters ==

* '''1''' &ndash; section name of the Talk page discussion to link to (optional; no default)
* '''reason''' &ndash; your justification for placing the template  (optional; no default) 

== Redirects ==
* {{tl|Weight}}

== See also ==
* {{tl|Undue weight}}
* {{tl|Undue weight section}}
{{Dispute templates}}

<includeonly>{{Sandbox other||
[[Category:Inline dispute templates]]
[[Category:Neutrality templates]]
}}</includeonly> 
<templatedata>
{
	"params": {
		"1": {
			"aliases": [
				"date"
			],
			"label": "Month and year",
			"type": "string",
			"autovalue": "May 2025",
			"suggested": true,
			"description": "The month and year of when the tag was added.",
			"example": "July 2023"
		},
		"reason": {
			"label": "Reason",
			"type": "string",
			"suggested": true,
			"description": "An optional explanation for why the tag has been added."
		}
	},
	"description": "This template adds an inline cleanup tag, questioning if a source has been given undue weight.",
	"format": "inline"
}
</templatedata>

